<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="flex-container"></div>
    <h1><%= address %></h1>
    <p>BLOG API: </p>
    <p>THE API PROTECTED USING TOKEN, GENERATE TOKEN AND SET HEADER {Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE for authorization</Token>`</p>
    <br>
    <a>GET <%= address %>/API/ - GET ALL BLOG POSTS</a>
    <br>
    <a>POST <%= address %>/API/ - CREATE BLOG POST</a>
    <br>
    <a>GET <%= address %>/API/:ID- GET BLOG POST DETAIL</a>
    <br>
    <a>GET <%= address %>/API/:ID/edit - GET EDIT BLOG POST FORM</a>
    <br>
    <a>PATCH <%= address %>/API/:ID/- EDIT INDIVIDUAL BLOG POST</a>
    <br>
    <a>DELETE <%= address %>/API/:ID - DELETE BLOG POST</a>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>COMMENTS API: </p>
    <br>
    <a>GET <%= address %>/API/:ID/comments - GET ALL COMMENTS OF A BLOG POST</a>
    <br>
    <a>POST <%= address %>/API/:ID/comments - CREATE NEW COMMENT</a>
    <br>
    <a>DELETE <%= address %>/API/:ID/comments/:ID - DELETE INDIVIDUAL COMMENT</a>
    <br>
    <a>GET <%= address %>/API/:ID/comments/:ID - GET INDIVIDUAL COMMENT DETAIL</a>
    <br>
    <a>PATCH <%= address %>/API/:ID/comments/:ID - UPDATE COMMENT</a>

    <p>COMMENTS API: </p>
    <br>
    <a>POST <%= address %>/users/ - to create user </a>
    <br>
    <a>POST <%= address %>/login/ - to generate JsonWebToken </a>
  </div>
  </body>
</html>
